    "body": "Hi Helder, The issue arises because your genesis file includes a rule for validating blocks - that they must have a blocktime of minimum 4 seconds, but the chain you are importing has blocks with only 3 seconds between them. \r\nYou can't increase blocktime, since this renders previous blocks invalid. Let us know if this is unclear to you from the documentation or if you expect a different result! If not, I'll go ahead and close this ticket.\r\n",
